[ANY CHAIN USER]
   ↓
Submit zk/multisig lockproof → KarrotEscrow
   ↓ emits →
   🔁 AssetLocked event
   ↓
Listener or relay mints `pxAsset` on PulseChain
   ↓
User swaps pxAsset on KarrotDEX Aggregator
   ↓
Price oracle fetches consensus price from MeshOracle
   ↓
When user wants to unlock → burns pxAsset → KarrotEscrow → SourceChain release
